# <type>(<scope>): <subject — lowercase, imperative, no trailing period>
#
# body: wrap at ~72 chars; lowercase sentences unless a proper noun requires caps.
#
# types: feat | fix | docs | chore | refactor | perf | test | ci | build
# scopes (examples): nimji | cli | config | deps | parser | transport | session
